WEBVTT

00:10.378 --> 00:13.678
It was causing wicked
hallucinations.

00:13.680 --> 00:17.750
My son -- I'm afraid he'll
be traumatized for life.

00:17.752 --> 00:21.954
He's trying to kill them.

00:21.956 --> 00:24.390
- He hits me.
- Yeah? Where does he hit you?

00:26.527 --> 00:28.193
Did you touch me?

00:29.363 --> 00:31.729
He pulled the trigger,
blew his head off.

00:32.900 --> 00:36.168
I'm thinking he killed himself.

00:36.170 --> 00:39.171
He's whispering, "You want
to kill everybody."

00:40.341 --> 00:42.875
Panic, panic, panic.

00:42.877 --> 00:44.777
My name is Amy Allan.

00:44.779 --> 00:46.611
I'm seeing, like, blood.

00:46.613 --> 00:49.915
The house just feels <i> bad.</i>

00:49.917 --> 00:51.183
I see dead people.

00:51.185 --> 00:55.554
This man
is <i> completely</i> insane.

00:55.556 --> 00:58.724
I speak to dead people...

00:58.726 --> 01:00.893
Whoo. Okay.
She doesn't like it in there.

01:00.895 --> 01:02.895
...and they speak to me.

01:02.897 --> 01:04.930
He likes to twist that knife.

01:04.932 --> 01:08.500
But there's only one way to know
if my findings are real.

01:08.502 --> 01:12.170
Something paranormal
is trying to kill them.

01:12.172 --> 01:13.639
I rely on my partner.

01:13.641 --> 01:15.174
I'm Steve Di Schiavi.

01:15.176 --> 01:17.509
I'm a retired New York City
homicide detective.

01:17.511 --> 01:19.144
Now does he die right there,
on the spot?

01:19.146 --> 01:23.081
I know every person,
every house has secrets.

01:23.083 --> 01:25.717
I think it's trying
to steal my soul.

01:25.719 --> 01:27.553
It's my job to reveal them.

01:27.555 --> 01:29.855
You ever get touched
like that again?

01:29.857 --> 01:31.757
But Steve and I never speak...

01:31.759 --> 01:33.825
We never communicate
during an investigation.

01:33.827 --> 01:35.160
...until the very end.

01:35.162 --> 01:37.329
I'm as stunned as you guys are.

01:37.331 --> 01:39.264
When we uncover if
it's safe for you to stay...

01:39.266 --> 01:41.900
I don't want anything
to happen to my daughter.

01:41.902 --> 01:43.335
Or time to get out.

01:43.337 --> 01:46.672
His goal
is to kill you guys.

