02:38.926 --> 02:41.059
When I'm finished,
the location will be ready

02:41.061 --> 02:42.594
for tonight's walk.

02:51.739 --> 02:54.473
Yeah, this is not good.

02:54.475 --> 02:56.207
I hear yelling.

02:56.209 --> 02:59.678
People are dealing
